9ef1bfb9-2afc-472b-a088-6f5e3fa14d52.title: Note
9ef1bfb9-2afc-472b-a088-6f5e3fa14d52.text: (COMBAT) Missing getting items and talking again

956e2135-df96-4323-953f-d6fac8bd1a04.title: Combat Instructor
956e2135-df96-4323-953f-d6fac8bd1a04.text:
Do I look like I care? To me you're just another
newcomer who thinks they're ready to fight.

8534ad1d-cdeb-45b1-9697-daedc01db5b0.title: <player>
8534ad1d-cdeb-45b1-9697-daedc01db5b0.text: I already have this Bronze Dagger.

8e6966f9-6088-4c07-9284-aa9711a76e9c.title: Note
8e6966f9-6088-4c07-9284-aa9711a76e9c.text: Might be different if dropped dagger?

32743c57-2aef-403d-933e-244221693f0f.title: Combat Instructor
32743c57-2aef-403d-933e-244221693f0f.text:
Very good, but that little butter knife isn't going to
protect you much. Here, take these.

args: Kill a rat with your sword
&aEquip your sword and shield by shift clicking in inventory

3f3f60b0-1b1a-4b9b-9379-8b9b9020d837.title: <player>
3f3f60b0-1b1a-4b9b-9379-8b9b9020d837.text: I did it! I killed a giant rat.

ff429c81-e535-461c-bb27-73418f8964ff.title: Combat Instructor
ff429c81-e535-461c-bb27-73418f8964ff.text:
I saw, <player>. You seem better at this than I
thought. Now that you have grasped the basic swordplay,
let's move on.

89b92f56-149b-411e-8d74-7474bb838fa3.title: Combat Instructor
89b92f56-149b-411e-8d74-7474bb838fa3.text:
Let's try some ranged attacking, with this you can kill
foes from a distance. Also, foes unable to reach you are
as good as dead. You'll be able to attack the rats
without entering the pit.

args: Kill a rat with your bow
&aEquip your bow and arrows by shift clicking in inventory

835993a7-48da-4a04-9a6a-45bba1e93c93.title: Combat Instructor
835993a7-48da-4a04-9a6a-45bba1e93c93.text:
Talk to me again after you kill a Giant Rat with that
bow I gave you.

7ea5a220-cfd2-4dd7-bffd-957d9132657c.title: <player>
7ea5a220-cfd2-4dd7-bffd-957d9132657c.text: Tell me about combat stats again.

options.text: Tell me about melee combat again.
Tell me about ranged combat again.
Nope, I'm ready to move on!

6d84e6a7-dd96-406b-adda-9ab155ea8ad4.title: Combat Instructor
6d84e6a7-dd96-406b-adda-9ab155ea8ad4.text:
Certainly. You have three main combat stats: Strength,
Defence and Attack.

023c23bd-7a23-4df0-aedf-25b1c86b4f5e.title: Combat Instructor
023c23bd-7a23-4df0-aedf-25b1c86b4f5e.text:
Strength determines the maximum hit you will be able
to deal with your blows, Defence determines the amount
of damage you will be able to defend and Attack
determines the accuracy of your blows.

3c85a60f-bab9-43fe-a5ef-8241dc70546d.title: Combat Instructor
3c85a60f-bab9-43fe-a5ef-8241dc70546d.text:
Other stats are used in combat such as Prayer,
Hitpoints, Magic and Ranged. All these stats can go
towards determining your combat level, which is shown
near the top of your combat interface screen.

4837fe32-e2e4-4e7a-9d32-8822a995f450.title: Combat Instructor
4837fe32-e2e4-4e7a-9d32-8822a995f450.text:
You will found out on the mainland that certain items can
also affect your stats. There are potions that can be
drunk that can alter your stats temporarily, such as
raising Strength.

322e51b0-d2d7-4bb2-9381-49aabc9c42e4.title: Combat Instructor
322e51b0-d2d7-4bb2-9381-49aabc9c42e4.text:
You will also raise your Defence and Attack values by
using different weapons and armours.

3e1980ea-c582-446f-9f6d-41a657b62059.title: Combat Instructor
3e1980ea-c582-446f-9f6d-41a657b62059.text:
Before going into combat with an opponent it is wise to
put the mouse over them and see what combat level
they are.

6f3f1d91-fd0c-4478-b216-df6fc65db4ea.title: Combat Instructor
6f3f1d91-fd0c-4478-b216-df6fc65db4ea.text:
Green coloured writing usually means it will be an easy
fight for you, red means you will probably lose, yellow
means they are around your level and orange means
they are slightly stronger.

2ca23c03-a52a-449b-b622-fbd3d2b53ecd.title: Combat Instructor
2ca23c03-a52a-449b-b622-fbd3d2b53ecd.text:
Sometimes things will go your way, sometimes they
won't. There is no such thing as a guaranteed win, but
if the odds are on your side, you stand the best chance
of walking away victorious.

acd059c2-1000-4987-ad5d-04b358fa5f8e.title: Combat Instructor
acd059c2-1000-4987-ad5d-04b358fa5f8e.text:
Now, was there something else you wanted to hear
about again?

52db6e6b-32eb-4b11-a41e-36f0948e16e3.title: <player>
52db6e6b-32eb-4b11-a41e-36f0948e16e3.text: Tell me about melee combat again.

2d6e1d76-366d-405d-a0c4-b66a1b45b52b.title: Combat Instructor
2d6e1d76-366d-405d-a0c4-b66a1b45b52b.text:
Ah, my speciality, Close combat fighting, which is also
known as melee fighting, covers all combat done at close
range to your opponent.

a3762d4a-ba1b-4bdc-952b-78fcfdd816a9.title: Combat Instructor
a3762d4a-ba1b-4bdc-952b-78fcfdd816a9.text:
Melee fighting depends entirely upon your three basic
combat stats: Attack, Defence, and Strength.

177d183a-5771-46c4-ac64-3009c996ae9b.title: Combat Instructor
177d183a-5771-46c4-ac64-3009c996ae9b.text:
Also, of course, it depends on the quality of your
armour and weaponry, A high-levelled fighter with good
armour and weapons will be deadly up close.

3a0eea6c-1b5a-4c1f-8932-d6c5913c5f2c.title: Combat Instructor
3a0eea6c-1b5a-4c1f-8932-d6c5913c5f2c.text:
If this is the path you wish to take, remember your
success depends on getting as close yo your enemy as
quickly as possible.

6515c601-ecca-4a11-8b77-a308e7ac4156.title: Combat Instructor
6515c601-ecca-4a11-8b77-a308e7ac4156.text:
Personally, I consider the fine art of melee combat to
be the ONLY combat method worth using.

c87879a0-e7e8-4d6a-8c62-61ecfcc3114f.title: <player>
c87879a0-e7e8-4d6a-8c62-61ecfcc3114f.text: Tell me about ranged combat again.

a1cee4b2-bd60-49d6-80bf-b664b5a904e0.title: Combat Instructor
a1cee4b2-bd60-49d6-80bf-b664b5a904e0.text:
Thinking of being a ranger, eh? Well, okay. I don't
enjoy it myself, but I can see the appeal.

34d3e62e-4025-4c60-b175-9592ddec83bc.title: Combat Instructor
34d3e62e-4025-4c60-b175-9592ddec83bc.text:
Ranging employ a lot of different weapons as a skill,
not just the shortbow you have there. Spears, throwing
knives, and crossbows are all used best at a distance
from your enemy.

3c9a0e4f-ba8c-4899-8cf3-0fed776baf5c.title: Combat Instructor
3c9a0e4f-ba8c-4899-8cf3-0fed776baf5c.text:
Now, those rats were easy pickings, but on the
mainland you will be very lucky if you can find a spot
where you can shoot at your enemies without them
being able to retaliate.

d8309baf-236f-434f-9c3f-61962412b806.title: Combat Instructor
d8309baf-236f-434f-9c3f-61962412b806.text:
At close range, rangers often do badly in combat. Your
best tactic as a ranger is to hit and run, keeping your
foe at a distance.

3c19a75c-2f67-4d5a-b9c8-5ac2158f5fdd.title: Combat Instructor
3c19a75c-2f67-4d5a-b9c8-5ac2158f5fdd.text:
You effectiveness as a ranger is almost entirely
dependent on your Ranged stat. As with all skills, the
more your train it, the more powerful it will become.

3bd731c5-fb8d-4394-8dfa-3f36ede5a16b.title: Combat Instructor
3bd731c5-fb8d-4394-8dfa-3f36ede5a16b.text: Anything else you wanted to know?

bca89415-610b-4a1c-a9e3-bb0327564237.title: <player>
bca89415-610b-4a1c-a9e3-bb0327564237.text: Tell me about the Wilderness again.

20a10bdd-410a-4582-bee0-50ada1c660b6.title: Combat Instructor
20a10bdd-410a-4582-bee0-50ada1c660b6.text:
Ah yes, the Wilderness, It is a place of evil, mark my
words. Many is the colleague I have lost in that foul
place.

0fe18e06-3058-4f3a-ac84-128198aeee3c.title: Combat Instructor
0fe18e06-3058-4f3a-ac84-128198aeee3c.text:
It is also a place of both adventure and wealth, so if
you are brave enough and strong enough to survive it,
you will make a killing. Literally!

595d6dc0-893a-4af5-8cfe-b27910c46bc8.title: Combat Instructor
595d6dc0-893a-4af5-8cfe-b27910c46bc8.text:
It is also the only place in the land of RuneScape
where players are able to attack each other at will, and
as such is the haunt of many Player Killers, or P'Kers
if you will.

5220f030-0939-448e-bc1f-7e06b558804d.title: Combat Instructor
5220f030-0939-448e-bc1f-7e06b558804d.text:
There are few things different in the Wilderness in
comparison to the rest of the land of RuneScape.
Firstly, as I just mentioned, you can and will be
attacked by other players.

889429fa-98a8-427a-b2be-26c84f996508.title: Combat Instructor
889429fa-98a8-427a-b2be-26c84f996508.text:
For this reason, you will be given a warning when you
approach the Wilderness, as it is not a place you would
wish to enter by accident.

fb38c42d-d55b-45d5-a6ac-af0341bd5662.title: Combat Instructor
fb38c42d-d55b-45d5-a6ac-af0341bd5662.text:
Secondly, there are a number of 'levels' to it. The
further into it you travel, the greater the range of
people you can attack.

584b5a60-8770-42c0-99b8-7f24833f5aa7.title: Combat Instructor
584b5a60-8770-42c0-99b8-7f24833f5aa7.text:
In level 1 wilderness you will only be able to attack, or
be attacked by, those players withing one combat level of
yourself.

bf186ad3-c200-4e40-bd5b-d50a4df0c885.title: Combat Instructor
bf186ad3-c200-4e40-bd5b-d50a4df0c885.text:
In level 50, any player within fifty levels, of you will be
able to attack, or be attack by you. Always keep an
eye on what level of the Wilderness you are currently
in.

650de68f-8d54-4366-af4a-a9080fd5e950.title: Combat Instructor
650de68f-8d54-4366-af4a-a9080fd5e950.text:
Your current Wilderness level is shown at the bottom
right of the screen. The final thing you should know
about the Wilderness is being 'skulled'.

529309b8-df95-4839-b6e3-544fdb2bb7c9.title: Combat Instructor
529309b8-df95-4839-b6e3-544fdb2bb7c9.text:
If you attack another player with them having
attacked first, you will gain a skull above your
characters head.

d843b9ec-ccc8-4e2c-bf1c-36c2543da310.title: Combat Instructor
d843b9ec-ccc8-4e2c-bf1c-36c2543da310.text:
What this means is that if you die while skulled, you will
lose EVERYTHING that your character was carrying.

6a03d49b-e9cd-4180-8f2c-ac1f5e91ed1d.title: Combat Instructor
6a03d49b-e9cd-4180-8f2c-ac1f5e91ed1d.text:
When skulled, you should try to avoid dying for the
twenty minutes or so it will take for the skull to wear
off.

811ea3e1-c5f2-4fc8-8afb-d03111fcfa9c.title: Combat Instructor
811ea3e1-c5f2-4fc8-8afb-d03111fcfa9c.text:
If you wish to find the Wilderness, head north from
where you start on the mainland. It is rather large and
hard to miss.

5e278cda-f4f6-4416-9950-bb558df293a7.title: Combat Instructor
5e278cda-f4f6-4416-9950-bb558df293a7.text:
If you don't wish to end up there, take notice of the
warning you will receive when getting near to it.
